		  <div class="__pf" id="__pf"><div class="pf-55296f5c sc-hwwEjo kIFSBP" data-pf-type="Body"><div class="pf-f609988a sc-kUaPvJ gjMMZr" data-pf-type="Layout"><div data-container="true" class="pf-97693627 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-9070797f pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-32b812ac sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h1 mode="view" class="pf-9efa5559 sc-epnACN iUKiYr" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-43623e08 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">THE BARN is now cash free<br></span></h1><p class="pf-301311ad sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-fd3675ee sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">We decided to make all our operations completely cash free. While cafés in Berlin and Germany as a whole are often still working on a cash only basis, we felt strongly about being a leading example to promote a cash free business. Here is why:&nbsp;<br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-6876e1a5 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-36c70a2b pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-f6fb7571 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h4 mode="view" class="pf-215f431c sc-iQNlJl joTjoi" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-d86c0681 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">SAFETY FIRST<br></span></h4><p class="pf-fcc28caa sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-e9428a71 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">By not having a drawer full of cash we make our cafés a lot safer for our staff and customers. There were several places in our neighbourhoods that were targeted by criminals, especially in winter when it is dark at closing time. Walking coins and cash to and from our bank was another moment of risk that we felt uncomfortable with. The safety of our staff is of utmost importance to us.<br></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-56720aea sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-45a0a7b8 sc-iyvyFf gJXqlU" data-pf-type="Block"></div><p class="pf-04c475be sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-d748580e sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Our Hackescher Markt location<br><a href="https://thebarn.de/pages/s12" target="_blank" style="font-style: italic; text-decoration-line: underline;">Neue Schönhauser Straße 12, 10178 Berlin</a></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-98e38583 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-eb13acf2 pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-673ed4f0 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-60686333 sc-iyvyFf gJXqlU" data-pf-type="Block"></div><p class="pf-a7357945 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-1473c3e6 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Our latest opening: THE BARN Nordbahnhof<br><a href="https://thebarn.de/pages/i112" style="text-decoration-line: underline;">&nbsp;<span style="font-style: italic;">Invalidenstraße 112, 10115 Berlin</span></a></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-b4e6e57d sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h4 mode="view" class="pf-0fd0dc44 sc-iQNlJl joTjoi" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-539f8a77 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Convenience<br></span></h4><p class="pf-524eff50 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-48fef079 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">We know how annoying it is to order that delicious coffee or grab a bag of beans - and then realise that you do not have enough cash. We take all cards and various electronic payments via your smartphone - easy. There is no minimum purchase amount either, and no extra costs!<br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-af19cc07 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-dd3ecb88 pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-b2e981dc sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h4 mode="view" class="pf-f18232b3 sc-iQNlJl joTjoi" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-98da612d sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Loyalty Cards<br></span></h4><p class="pf-bdc90b31 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-2b684fbd sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">All our cafés hand out black gift cards. They can be loaded with credit for purchases, and they double as a loyalty card too. Using this card when buying your coffee, you collect a digital stamp – after eight coffees you’ll get one free. You can order and load one of these cards via our <a href="https://thebarn.de/collections/vouchers/products/giftcard-cafe" target="_blank">webshop</a>, or ask our staff next time you visit. <br></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-8fb725a3 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-9ea44362 sc-iyvyFf gJXqlU" data-pf-type="Block"></div><p class="pf-97b027ec sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-a4b6eaae sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">The little Barn opened in 2010 in Mitte and enjoys a loyal customer base<br><span style="font-style: italic; text-decoration-line: underline;">Auguststraße 58, 10119 Berlin</span></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-881bd3e4 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-8ed4dfbd pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-e542e64e sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-8bf37685 sc-iyvyFf gJXqlU" data-pf-type="Block"></div><p class="pf-8d480229 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-e7be20d0 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Our Potsdamer Platz café sits in the historic Weinhaus Huth<br><span style="font-style: italic; text-decoration-line: underline;">Alte Potsdamer Straße 5, 10785 Berlin</span></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-ea0e4758 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h4 mode="view" class="pf-d9a8947f sc-iQNlJl joTjoi" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-700be5ef sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Hygiene & Workflow<br></span></h4><p class="pf-5ede5222 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-8e9e87fb sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">These points may sound minor, but we are big on hygiene and workflow. Touching coins and bills is not very hygienic - we find it a lot cleaner to handle a card from your wallet rather than cash that has been through many hands. Also, running out of coins and slowing down the purchasing process can slow down queues at our navigation points. <br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-03db1816 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-9e43696e pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-0f5c4ae3 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h4 mode="view" class="pf-534f13ed sc-iQNlJl joTjoi" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-1cf14669 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Clean Books<br></span></h4><p class="pf-e4275dff sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-ca236f2b sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Needless to add, but for us the registration and full insurance of all our staff had been no question from day one of THE BARN. We pay at least minimum wage and insure all our staff fully. While that is not common practise in many cafés we felt that a cashless business also signals that we do everything 150% by the book and that we look after our employees.&nbsp;<br></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-409dce2d sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-eca3aa5a sc-iyvyFf gJXqlU" data-pf-type="Block"></div><p class="pf-31e69d11 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-e8a93c19 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Café Kranzler is the most iconic "Kaffeehaus" in Berlin<br><span style="font-style: italic; text-decoration-line: underline;"><a href="http://https://thebarn.de/pages/k18" target="_blank">Kurfürstendamm 18, 10719 Berlin</a></span></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-cfff60ee sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-c67c3f79 pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-9e3d520f sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-266adb74 sc-iyvyFf gJXqlU" data-pf-type="Block"></div><p class="pf-13ce2ad4 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-b6a0c0d0 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Our Roastery is a destination for our international coffee community<br><span style="font-style: italic; text-decoration-line: underline;"><a href="https://thebarn.de/pages/s8" target="_blank">Schönhauser Allee 8, 10119 Berlin</a></span></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-807ce03e sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h4 mode="view" class="pf-9cb5c84a sc-iQNlJl joTjoi" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-22ee3d41 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">International Community<br></span></h4><p class="pf-feceb11e sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-fc846ec6 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">THE BARN is a destination for an international coffee community that comes to Berlin to visit us. Card payments are another way of making their visits even more convenient and cost effective. No longer will you have to search for an ATM with expensive transaction fees - when all you wanted was a cup of our coffee or buy a bag of freshly roasted beans. <br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-13582a8a sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-7ee33fa6 pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-f08af7f2 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><p class="pf-f0a0b6a2 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-7520c3e2 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">We are very much looking forward to your next visit - check out our <a href="https://thebarn.de/pages/locations" style="text-decoration-line: underline;" target="_blank">locations page</a> for more details.<br></span></p></div></div></div><div class="pf-ddef39d3 pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-dc21d6aa sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-802cd942 sc-iyvyFf gJXqlU" data-pf-type="Block"></div><p class="pf-b52822dc sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-5b0834f6 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Our beautiful space in Neukölln features a huge community table<br><span style="font-style: italic;"><a href="https://thebarn.de/pages/f27" target="_blank">Friedelstraße 27, 12047 Berlin</a></span></span></p></div></div></div><div class="pf-494a2cf4 pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-4ca6ad3c sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><a class="pf-d3fb589d sc-kPVwWT dOgkyj" href="https://thebarn.de/blogs/the-barn-blog" target="_self" data-pf-type="Button"><span class="pf-0988df30 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">BACK TO THE BLOG</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script>
